# Environment Variables for Vercel Deploy
# Copy these EXACTLY as they are written below

# Supabase Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_project_url_here
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Go to your Supabase dashboard
# 2. Find your Project URL in Settings > API
# 3. Find your Anon Key in Settings > API
# 4. Replace the values above with your actual values
# 5. Copy these variables to Vercel dashboard > Settings > Environment Variables
